  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl combine diced cucumber, tomatoes, sliced olives, onion, and capers.",
    "Add the drained herring pieces to the bowl and gently mix.",
    "Sprinkle chopped parsley and dill over the salad and toss to combine.",
    "Drizzle olive oil and lemon juice evenly, then season with salt and pepper.",
    "Let the salad rest for 5 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Serve chilled or at room temperature over a bed of mixed greens if desired."
